OL,3,CIllegal waste dumps to be cleared amid
OL,4,Ccrackdown on fly-tipping
OL,6,FSome of the worst illegal waste sites
OL,7,Fwhere thousands of tonnes of rubbish
OL,8,Fhave been dumped will be cleaned-up
OL,9,Fafter the government pledged to
OL,10,Fdirectly fund the operation.
OL,12,FThe move is part of a "zero-tolerance"
OL,13,Fnew action plan to tackle the #1
OL,14,Fbillion problem of waste crime, as
OL,15,Fofficials warn around a fifth of all
OL,16,Frubbish is illegally managed, with
OL,17,Fgangs behind it becoming increasingly
OL,18,Fsophisticated.
OL,26,@tD@WOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
