FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774023076
OL,3,CIllegal waste dumps to be cleared amid
OL,4,Ccrackdown on fly-tipping
OL,6,FIt comes in the wake of figures
OL,7,Fshowing fly-tipping on public land
OL,8,Fclimbed 9% in the past year, with
OL,9,Fsites in Wigan, Lancashire and
OL,10,FSheffield housing a combined 48,000
OL,11,Ftonnes of waste.
OL,13,FThe measures are part of a number by
OL,14,Fthe government to target illegal
OL,15,Fdumping and fly-tipping, including
OL,16,Fheavier punishments for offenders
OL,17,Fincluding cleaning the streets and
OL,18,Frepaying the cost of the waste they
OL,19,Fdumped.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
