OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774023076
OL,3,CIllegal waste dumps to be cleared amid
OL,4,Ccrackdown on fly-tipping
OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,7,Fsaid: "Waste criminals have been
OL,8,Fdamaging our communities, countryside,
OL,9,Fenvironment and economy for too long.
OL,11,F"This action plan sends a clear
OL,12,Fmessage: dump illegally and you will
OL,13,Fface the full consequences.
OL,15,F"We will give enforcement officers new
OL,16,Fpolice-style powers to bring offenders
OL,17,Fto justice."
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUwD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
