PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774023076
OL,3,CIllegal waste dumps to be cleared amid
OL,4,Ccrackdown on fly-tipping
OL,6,FArea environment manager Mark Easedale
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have immense sympathy for
OL,8,Fthe local community affected by this
OL,9,Fwaste crime, which continues to have
OL,10,Fan impact on the people who live and
OL,11,Fwork in the area.
OL,13,F"We are doing everything within our
OL,14,Fpowers to identify the perpetrators,
OL,15,Fincluding launching a major criminal
OL,16,Finvestigation and interviewing
OL,17,Findividuals under caution."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
