OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774023076
OL,3,CIllegal waste dumps to be cleared amid
OL,4,Ccrackdown on fly-tipping
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency said a "number
OL,7,Fof individuals" had been interviewed
OL,8,Funder caution and formal notices have
OL,9,Fbeen served requiring the waste to be
OL,10,Fremoved, as well as notices served
OL,11,Frequiring further information.
OL,13,FThe agency has already conducted
OL,14,Fpreliminary assessments of these
OL,15,Fsites, with further clean-up
OL,16,Fassessments to come.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
