OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774023076
OL,3,CIllegal waste dumps to be cleared amid
OL,4,Ccrackdown on fly-tipping
OL,6,FIn January, Greater Manchester Mayor
OL,7,FAndy Burnham said he believed the tip
OL,8,Fwas "linked to more serious criminal
OL,9,Fgang-related activity" and called on
OL,10,Fthe National Crime Agency to intervene.
OL,12,FThe government is forcing fly-tippers
OL,13,Fto pay to clean up illegal waste
OL,14,Fsites, it will also introduce a
OL,15,FLandfill Tax rebate for local
OL,16,Fauthorities that step up to clear
OL,17,Fsites, easing financial pressures on
OL,18,Fauthorities.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
